### Crear nueva reparación (Ingreso a taller)
# @name createRepair
POST {{baseUrl}}/repairs
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "ownerId": "69e282ce1aeabeda159f263c",
  "brand": "Dell",
  "model": "Inspiron 15",
  "serialNumber": "SN-DELL-9988",
  "faultDescription": "No da imagen, el fan gira al máximo.",
  "specifications": {
    "processor": "i5 11va Gen",
    "ram": "8GB",
    "storage": "256GB SSD"
  }
}

### Listar todas las reparaciones (Dashboard)
GET {{baseUrl}}/repairs
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### Actualizar estado (Cambiar a "En Diagnóstico")
@repairId = {{createRepair.response.body._id}}
PUT {{baseUrl}}/repairs/{{repairId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "DIAGNOSING",
  "description": "Se desarma equipo para medir tensiones en placa madre.",
  "diagnostic": "Cortocircuito aparente en línea de 19V.",
  "category": "Motherboard"
}